# Interactive regex editor
---

A small and simple tool that allow you to use python regex over an interactive shell.
![Demo](./docs/usage.gif)

# Installation
---
```bash
pip install rexi
```

# Usage
---
```bash
cat /etc/hosts | rexi
```


